query:
INSERT INTO iot_devices (device_code, device_name, device_type, protocol, status, is_active, last_heartbeat) 
VALUES 
('TEMP-001', 'Temperature Sensor A1', 'sensor', 'mqtt', 'online', 1, NOW()),
('PRESS-002', 'Pressure Sensor B2', 'sensor', 'http', 'online', 1, NOW()),
('VIB-003', 'Vibration Monitor C3', 'sensor', 'mqtt', 'error', 1, DATE_SUB(NOW(), INTERVAL 5 MINUTE)),
('PWR-004', 'Power Meter D4', 'sensor', 'tcp', 'offline', 1, DATE_SUB(NOW(), INTERVAL 2 HOUR))
ON DUPLICATE KEY UPDATE last_heartbeat = NOW();
